description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Full Body Calisthenics Workout - Follow Along At Home - Beginner and Intermediate // Lucy Lismore' from the channel Lucy Lismore.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Today's workout is a follow along full body calisthenics workout suitable for beginners and intermediates. It might be slightly on the challenging side for some beginners but don't be afraid to modify anything you need to.

There are 3 rounds in total and the exercises will increase in difficulty each round so you have several options to choose from!
